                    </p>
                    <div class="d-flex gap-3 fs-5">
                        <a class="footer-link" href="https://github.com/mousaalbadwi/" target="_blank" aria-label="GitHub"><i class="bi bi-github"></i></a>
                        <a class="footer-link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mousa-mustafa-798822277/" target="_blank" aria-label="LinkedIn"><i class="bi bi-linkedin"></i></a>
                        <a class="footer-link" href="mailto:moeyad2003@gmail.com" aria-label="Email"><i class="bi bi-envelope"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-6 col-md-4 col-lg-2">
                    <h6 class="fw-bold mb-3">Explore</h6>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled d-grid gap-2">
                        <li><a class="footer-link" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">Home</a></li>
                        <li><a class="footer-link" asp-controller="Projects" asp-action="Index">Projects</a></li>
                        <li><a class="footer-link" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="About">About</a></li>
                        <li><a class="footer-link" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Contact">Contact</a></li>
                        <li><a class="footer-link" href="~/files/CV.pdf" download="Mousa_CV.pdf">Download CV</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="col-6 col-md-4 col-lg-3">
                    <h6 class="fw-bold mb-3">Tech Stack</h6>
                    <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                        <span class="badge text-bg-light border">ASP.NET Core</span>
                        <span class="badge text-bg-light border">EF Core</span>
                        <span class="badge text-bg-light border">SQL Server</span>
                        <span class="badge text-bg-light border">Bootstrap</span>
